[
  {
    "start": 0.8,
    "end": 5.6,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hello, {Halloween|ハロウィン} is very {popular|人気の/有名な} in the {United States|アメリカ合衆国|/jəˈnaɪtɪd steɪts/|I live in the United States}."
  },
  {
    "start": 5.6,
    "end": 7.92,
    "text": "**Anna:** Children {trick or treat|お菓子をもらう習慣}"
  },
  {
    "start": 8.04,
    "end": 10.44,
    "text": "**Anna:** They ask people for {candy|お菓子/甘いもの}."
  },
  {
    "start": 10.44,
    "end": 15.48,
    "text": "**Anna:** Children and adults wear {costumes|仮装/衣装} and go to {parties|パーティー}."
  },
  {
    "start": 15.48,
    "end": 19.4,
    "text": "**Anna:** In fact, there is a Halloween {party|パーティー/集会} {tonight|今夜}."
  },
  {
    "start": 19.4,
    "end": 21.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** I need my friend Jeannie"
  },
  {
    "start": 21.82,
    "end": 24.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** Jeannie!"
  },
  {
    "start": 24.3,
    "end": 25.34,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hi!"
  },
  {
    "start": 25.34,
    "end": 26.619,
    "text": "**Genie:** Hi Anna!"
  },
  {
    "start": 26.619,
    "end": 28.06,
    "text": "**Genie:** What do you {need|必要とする/求める}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 28.06,
    "end": 30.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** Tonight there is a Halloween party."
  },
  {
    "start": 30.46,
    "end": 31.98,
    "text": "**Genie:** I love Halloween!"
  },
  {
    "start": 31.98,
    "end": 33.02,
    "text": "**Genie:** Are you going?"
  },
  {
    "start": 33.18,
    "end": 34.38,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might go"
  },
  {
    "start": 34.72,
    "end": 36.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might not go."
  },
  {
    "start": 36.56,
    "end": 39.12,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** I don't have a {costume|仮装/衣装}."
  },
  {
    "start": 39.12,
    "end": 41.04,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** Can you help me?"
  },
  {
    "start": 41.04,
    "end": 42.88,
    "text": "**Genie:** Dress as a {genie|精霊/魔法使い}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 42.88,
    "end": 44.24,
    "text": "**Anna:** Great idea!"
  },
  {
    "start": 44.24,
    "end": 46.72,
    "text": "**Anna:** I can do a genie {trick|トリック/魔法}."
  },
  {
    "start": 46.26,
    "end": 50.1,
    "text": "**Genie:** Like read {minds|心/精神}, Anna, be careful."
  },
  {
    "start": 50.1,
    "end": 52.18,
    "text": "**Genie:** Things might go wrong."
  },
  {
    "start": 52.18,
    "end": 54.019,
    "text": "**Anna:** What could go wrong"
  },
  {
    "start": 54.32,
    "end": 57.12,
    "text": "**Genie:** Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 57.12,
    "end": 60.96,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hey, look, I'm a genie."
  },
  {
    "start": 60.96,
    "end": 64.479,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is going to be {fun|楽しい}."
  },
  {
    "start": 63.88,
    "end": 70.28,
    "text": "**Genie:** Remember, Ama, be careful."
  },
  {
    "start": 70.28,
    "end": 72.6,
    "text": "**Anna:** Don't worry, Jeannie, I will"
  },
  {
    "start": 73,
    "end": 74.12,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** Excuse me?"
  },
  {
    "start": 74.12,
    "end": 76.2,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** Are you really a {mind reader|読心者/超能力者}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 76.2,
    "end": 77.88,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might be."
  },
  {
    "start": 77.88,
    "end": 79.64,
    "text": "**Genie:** Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 79.64,
    "end": 81.32,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** Tell me what I'm {thinking|考えている}."
  },
  {
    "start": 81.32,
    "end": 82.2,
    "text": "**Anna:** Sure."
  },
  {
    "start": 82.2,
    "end": 84.6,
    "text": "**Anna:** First, what do you {do|する/職業}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 84.6,
    "end": 85.479,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** I study."
  },
  {
    "start": 85.479,
    "end": 87.64,
    "text": "**Anna:** I'm a {junior|3年生/大学3年生} in college."
  },
  {
    "start": 87.72,
    "end": 89.32,
    "text": "**Anna:** What do you study?"
  },
  {
    "start": 89.32,
    "end": 91.24,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** I study {journalism|ジャーナリズム/報道}."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.24,
    "end": 92.2,
    "text": "**Genie:** Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 92.2,
    "end": 93.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** Wait."
  },
  {
    "start": 93.8,
    "end": 95.08,
    "text": "**Anna:** You are thinking"
  },
  {
    "start": 95.82,
    "end": 99.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** You will {graduate|卒業する} from college in about one year."
  },
  {
    "start": 99.98,
    "end": 101.82,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** Well yeah, that's the plan."
  },
  {
    "start": 101.82,
    "end": 104.54,
    "text": "**Anna:** I told you I'm a junior in college."
  },
  {
    "start": 104.16,
    "end": 105.04,
    "text": "**Anna:** Alright."
  },
  {
    "start": 105.04,
    "end": 107.6,
    "text": "**Anna:** Um wait, there's more."
  },
  {
    "start": 107.6,
    "end": 114.32,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** You are thinking you might get a job {writing|書く/執筆する} the news"
  },
  {
    "start": 114.64,
    "end": 117.52,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** I might get a job writing the news."
  },
  {
    "start": 117.52,
    "end": 118.64,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might?"
  },
  {
    "start": 118.64,
    "end": 120.24,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** That means I might not."
  },
  {
    "start": 120.24,
    "end": 122.48,
    "text": "**Anna:** And I'm studying really hard."
  },
  {
    "start": 122.48,
    "end": 123.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** No, no, no, no."
  },
  {
    "start": 123.68,
    "end": 124.16,
    "text": "**Anna:** Uh"
  },
  {
    "start": 124.16,
    "end": 129.119,
    "text": "**Anna:** No, you will, you will get a job {writing|書く/執筆する} the news."
  },
  {
    "start": 129.119,
    "end": 130.08,
    "text": "**Anna:** I will?"
  },
  {
    "start": 130.08,
    "end": 131.6,
    "text": "**Anna:** You will."
  },
  {
    "start": 131.6,
    "end": 132.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** I will."
  },
  {
    "start": 132.8,
    "end": 133.44,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** I think"
  },
  {
    "start": 135.98,
    "end": 137.5,
    "text": "**Anna:** Bye."
  },
  {
    "start": 137.5,
    "end": 140.379,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** Can you really {read|読む/理解する|/riːd/|I read books every day.} {minds|心/精神|/maɪndz/|What's on your mind?}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 140.379,
    "end": 142.54,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might."
  },
  {
    "start": 142.54,
    "end": 148.3,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** Well, today I will {ask|尋ねる/頼む|/æsk/|Can I ask you a question?} my {girlfriend|彼女|/ˈgɜːrlˌfrend/|My girlfriend is smart.} to marry me."
  },
  {
    "start": 148.32,
    "end": 150.24,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** What am I thinking?"
  },
  {
    "start": 150.24,
    "end": 153.92,
    "text": "**Anna:** Wait."
  },
  {
    "start": 153.92,
    "end": 161.12,
    "text": "**Anna:** You are thinking you might have a {wedding|結婚式|/ˈwedɪŋ/|We had a beautiful wedding.} very soon."
  },
  {
    "start": 161.54,
    "end": 167.299,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** Might {might|かもしれない|/maɪt/|She might come today.} she won't say no, will she?"
  },
  {
    "start": 167.299,
    "end": 170.18,
    "text": "**Anna:** No, no, she will say yes"
  },
  {
    "start": 170.62,
    "end": 174.06,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** I will have a {wedding|結婚式|/ˈwedɪŋ/|Our wedding was amazing.}, won't I?"
  },
  {
    "start": 174.06,
    "end": 176.78,
    "text": "**Anna:** You will."
  },
  {
    "start": 176.78,
    "end": 178.46,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** Thanks."
  },
  {
    "start": 178.46,
    "end": 179.74,
    "text": "**Rebecca:** I think."
  },
  {
    "start": 180.38,
    "end": 181.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** Good luck."
  },
  {
    "start": 182.74,
    "end": 184.34,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is {hard|難しい/厳しい|/hɑːrd/|Math is hard for me.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 184.98,
    "end": 187.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** Jeannie!"
  },
  {
    "start": 189.54,
    "end": 190.42,
    "text": "**Anna:** Uh-huh."
  },
  {
    "start": 190.42,
    "end": 192.02,
    "text": "**Genie:** What's wrong?"
  },
  {
    "start": 192.02,
    "end": 195.78,
    "text": "**Anna:** I don't want to be a {genie|精霊/魔法使い|/ˈdʒiːni/|The genie granted three wishes.} for Halloween."
  },
  {
    "start": 195.52,
    "end": 198.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might not go to the {party|パーティー|/ˈpɑːrti/|We had a fun party last night.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 198.8,
    "end": 201.599,
    "text": "**Genie:** Of course you will go."
  },
  {
    "start": 201.599,
    "end": 205.12,
    "text": "**Genie:** I have another {costume|衣装/コスチューム|/ˈkɒstjuːm/|She wore a beautiful costume.} for you."
  },
  {
    "start": 206,
    "end": 209.2,
    "text": "**Anna:** I'm a {rock star|ロックスター|/rɒk stɑːr/|He wants to be a rock star.}!"
  },
  {
    "start": 210.22,
    "end": 212.62,
    "text": "**Anna:** You read my mind!"
  },
  {
    "start": 212.62,
    "end": 216.54,
    "text": "**Genie:** No, you told me you like rock music."
  },
  {
    "start": 216.54,
    "end": 218.22,
    "text": "**Anna:** Oh, right."
  },
  {
    "start": 218.22,
    "end": 219.579,
    "text": "**Anna:** Well I love it!"
  },
  {
    "start": 219.579,
    "end": 220.86,
    "text": "**Genie:** Have fun, Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 220.86,
    "end": 221.98,
    "text": "**Kaveh:** Thanks, Jeannie"
  },
  {
    "start": 223.44,
    "end": 226.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** I am ready for the Halloween {party|パーティー|/ˈpɑːrti/|Let's have a party tonight.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 227.84,
    "end": 231.2,
    "text": "**Anna:** But I am not going to read minds."
  },
  {
    "start": 231.02,
    "end": 236.459,
    "text": "**Anna:** I might {play|演奏する/弾く|/pleɪ/|I play guitar every day.} some {rock|ロック音楽|/rɒk/|Rock music is very loud.} music."
  },
  {
    "start": 236.459,
    "end": 238.379,
    "text": "**Anna:** Or I might not."
  },
  {
    "start": 238.379,
    "end": 240.22,
    "text": "**Anna:** Till {next|次の/次|/nekst/|Next week is my birthday.} time."
  }
]
